messages.message: How did you stumbled across me on Linkedin?
Showed up in my feed probably one of our mutual connections. I've been friending people with that CEO mindset.
How's it going at purpose pops?

Its going - a bunch of learning lessons in 2016! 

What about you, what are you up to?

Just started at champagne Charlie's. Working on sosmethod.herokuapp.com on the side. It's a meditation start up like calm or headspace. An angel is paying for it. Lots of learning in 2016 indeed, got laid off from an EdTech startup. The school system is taking too long for us to get traction. Would have been nice to start taking market share away from Pearson though. :)

oh right on, always nice to have angels! What ed tech company? 

And thats a sharp site man - you doing all the building and UI / UX?

EdTech was called studysauce.com still up and running if you want to check it out. My partner did the designs I just do the implementation. Works well enough. Not totally happy with the animations yet.
gotcha cool cool - so you are more on the technical side than the design UI / UX side of things?
I guess so. I try to spend minimal time in Photoshop.

Gotcha - always nice to connect with solid developers! 

Stay in touch
